game.systems

Class OrderedEntityProcessingSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.artemis.BaseSystem
      • com.artemis.BaseEntitySystem
        • game.systems.OrderedEntityProcessingSystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.artemis.EntitySubscription.SubscriptionListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RenderingSystem

    public abstract class OrderedEntityProcessingSystem
extends com.artemis.BaseEntitySystem
implements com.artemis.EntitySubscription.SubscriptionListener
    Tracks a subset of entities, but does not implement any sorting or iteration.

    Like BaseEntitySystem, but uses Entity references instead of int.

    This system exists as a convenience for users migrating from other Artemis clones or older versions of odb. We recommend using the int systems over the Entity variants.

    Author:
    Arni Arent, Adrian Papari
